当地时间（[[UTC|UTC]]+11）2009年9月29日06:48:11，[[南太平洋|南太平洋]][[萨摩亚群岛|萨摩亚群岛]]和[[美属萨摩亚群岛|美属萨摩亚群岛]]之间海域发生[[震级|震级]]为8.1的[[地震|地震]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2009mdbi.php |title=Magnitude 8.0 - SAMOA ISLANDS REGION |date=2009-09-29 |publisher=earthquake.usgs.gov |accessdate=2009-09-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091007165801/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2009mdbi.php |archivedate=2009-10-07 }}</ref>地震引发的[[海啸|海啸]]袭击了萨摩亚、美属萨摩亚和[[汤加|汤加]]，对当地造成严重财产损失，旅游业也大受影响。目前已证实有超过189人在是次海啸中遇难，其中多数是在萨摩亚群岛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvnz.co.nz/national-news/search-continues-death-toll-rises-3045675|title=<!-- empty -->|accessdate=2009-10-02|archive-date=2009-10-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5kHDz9Yyt?url=http://tvnz.co.nz/national-news/search-continues-death-toll-rises-3045675|dead-url=no}}</ref>

